Incoming livestream: And then, bam, it works. And I think the killer application for this is in trusted execution environments, where people don't want to give you the code to run attestation over. What you can do is, you can load the model to become a private auditor and ask questions about the code base that is loaded inside, over which you can't compute hashes.

